data.description: This beautiful farmhouse is located in the Village of Ortonville and has all the modern updates you desire. Upon entering you'll find a spacious and inviting living room with plenty of natural light. The kitchen has been updated and features modern appliances, cabinets, and countertops with plenty of space for all your cooking needs. Off the kitchen you'll find an enclosed covered porch with leads to a huge deck for enjoying the outdoors. The dining room is perfect for entertaining guests or enjoying a quiet meal. The home features a spacious first floor master bedroom and an additional 3 bedrooms. The bonus outbuilding includes finished square footage with heat and A/C. This building has a living room, bedroom/office, kitchenette, and bathroom. The outbuilding also includes an area for a workshop and parking. Updates to the house include new roof (23), well (21), furnace (20), kitchen appliances and new washer/dryer. Great location close to all amenities including restaurants, shopping, and parks with an easy commute to the freeways. Do not miss your chance to own this beautiful home and all it has to offer!
